For unadventurous tourists abroad, a trip to Maccy D’s is usually the safe option if you don’t want to sample the local cuisine.

And with the golden arches springing up across the globe at an unprecedented rate, you can enjoy your Big Mac just about anywhere.

But don’t be fooled into thinking that McDonald's abroad is going to be exactly the same as it is back home; in fact different countries have their own additions to the menu, designed to appeal to local tastes.

